    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >欢迎加入我们的游戏讨论群</h2><br>官方玩家群：548253790<br>如加群时提示群已满，欢迎加入2群 ：996760787<br><br>我们期望听到你的声音!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法</h2><i>电兔拉比永远都在追求更强力更精准的跳跃！</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835670/extras/64ca2a7041cfadaef1a97095fe9f74cf.poster.avif?t=1772152418\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835670/extras/64ca2a7041cfadaef1a97095fe9f74cf.webm?t=1772152418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835670/extras/64ca2a7041cfadaef1a97095fe9f74cf.mp4?t=1772152418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>错误的把动作模块安装成发射模块，造就了拉比在所有机器人中最短但最强力的双腿，它早已习惯调动强大的双脚将自己发射出去，就像炮弹一样。依靠这一点，拉比踩踏敌人或附上墙壁时，同样可以获得巨大的反弹力道。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835670/extras/690c5d5a818be988475943fabc3d899c.poster.avif?t=1772152418\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835670/extras/690c5d5a818be988475943fabc3d899c.webm?t=1772152418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835670/extras/690c5d5a818be988475943fabc3d899c.mp4?t=1772152418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>更酷的是，拉比在冒险中获得“相位传送球”后，只要投的够远够准，就可以传送到任何地方。面对重重关卡与谜题，你可以全力冲刺配合二段跳控制身位，提前规划快速高效的路线；或者也可以像忍者一样冲刺加小跑，依靠反应即时躲避面前的各种危险。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏目标</h2><i>电兔拉比程序的核心——向往自由！</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835670/extras/4e277f736f1ef080bc3064d8c1a89b8a.poster.avif?t=1772152418\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835670/extras/4e277f736f1ef080bc3064d8c1a89b8a.webm?t=1772152418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835670/extras/4e277f736f1ef080bc3064d8c1a89b8a.mp4?t=1772152418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>游戏中你可以收集散落在关卡各处的“电池”，它们有的明晃晃的摆在必经之路上，有的则需要一些额外的探索精神。找到出口后，会根据收集到的电池数量结算宝石奖励，这些宝石将成为解锁新区域的钥匙。<br><br>除此之外，在一个关卡中集齐所有电池后，将会解锁该关卡的限时挑战。完成该挑战后会获得最后一颗“宝石”，这是为那些真正的挑战者准备的奖励！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><i>所有生灵都有其独到的价值，当然也包括机器人（只有可爱的才算）。</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835670/extras/dae755e57f6cffd0d171f0184f76ff11.poster.avif?t=1772152418\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835670/extras/dae755e57f6cffd0d171f0184f76ff11.webm?t=1772152418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835670/extras/dae755e57f6cffd0d171f0184f76ff11.mp4?t=1772152418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>上一秒的敌人可能会在下一瞬间成为你的朋友，它们虽然看起来凶巴巴的，但其实不会在意你在它们头上猛踩一脚。游戏中你可以操纵、挑衅甚至保护你的敌人，这往往会引出让你意想不到的通关方式。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏故事</h2><i>后启示录世界的虚幻与真实</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835670/extras/e8217ce2d51282cd52e4fbc0a98641a4.poster.avif?t=1772152418\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835670/extras/e8217ce2d51282cd52e4fbc0a98641a4.webm?t=1772152418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835670/extras/e8217ce2d51282cd52e4fbc0a98641a4.mp4?t=1772152418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>有没有好奇无数机器人的缔造者在哪？又为什么到处都在开动无意义的循环生产线？ <br><br>在巨大水果和呆萌机器人的奇幻之下，埋藏着关于人本身的真实故事。你可以小心探索，跃动在色彩明快、充满活力的卡通氛围中，与有趣的角色互动交流，一点点拼凑出这个世界的历史。来帮助主人公找到真正重要的事，去探寻被遗忘的一切，去拥抱真正的朋友！",
